issue.title: [CF 733] Text output bug of CLEU
issue.body:

comments.body:
I think it's EventTab's problem, not a really bug for CLEU.


> Posted by CurseForge user lsjyzjl

CLEU icons don't report any data until they are in use (they handle an event while TMW is locked), so the test event feature doesn't really work that well (at least for these particular tags).


> Posted by CurseForge user Cybeloras
